  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "给你一个盒子，要塞进尽可能多的同样大小的圆，你会怎么摆？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.11,
      "size": 33696,
      "text": "圆之间总会留下缝隙，塞得再挤也填不满整个盒子。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "我们用填充密度来衡量：圆的总面积，占盒子面积的比例。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "square",
      "line_id": "sq-1",
      "filename": "square-sq-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/square-sq-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.18,
      "size": 34848,
      "text": "最直觉的摆法是排成整齐的方格，一行行、一列列对齐。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "square",
      "line_id": "sq-2",
      "filename": "square-sq-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/square-sq-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.67,
      "size": 26784,
      "text": "每四个圆的中间，都空出一块弯曲的四角缝隙。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "square",
      "line_id": "sq-3",
      "filename": "square-sq-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/square-sq-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.1,
      "size": 33552,
      "text": "算下来密度约为百分之七十八点五,还有不少空间被浪费。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "hex",
      "line_id": "hex-1",
      "filename": "hex-hex-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/hex-hex-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.07,
      "size": 33120,
      "text": "把每一行错开半个圆,让上排的圆恰好卡进下排的凹槽。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "hex",
      "line_id": "hex-2",
      "filename": "hex-hex-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/hex-hex-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "这时每个圆被六个圆紧紧包围,像蜂巢一样严丝合缝。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "hex",
      "line_id": "hex-3",
      "filename": "hex-hex-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/hex-hex-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.16,
      "size": 34560,
      "text": "密度提升到约百分之九十点七,这是平面等圆填充的极限。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "random",
      "line_id": "rand-1",
      "filename": "random-rand-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/random-rand-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "如果不讲规则,随手把大小不一的圆丢进盒子会怎样?"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "random",
      "line_id": "rand-2",
      "filename": "random-rand-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/random-rand-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.24,
      "size": 35856,
      "text": "圆挤成一团,缝隙杂乱无章,密度往往明显低于规则排布。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.31,
      "size": 37008,
      "text": "切换方形、六边形、随机三种模式,盯住左上角的密度数字。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.96,
      "size": 31392,
      "text": "你会清楚看到六边形最密,方形次之,随机垫底。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.4,
      "size": 22320,
      "text": "填充密度衡量圆填满空间的效率。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "六边形最密堆积约九成密度,远胜方形与随机。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "circle-packing",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/circle-packing/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "蜜蜂和大自然早就懂得这个道理,我们下次再见!"
    }
